  <description><![CDATA[<p>The Äkäs Alp Apartments are the perfect choice for an atmospheric and family-friendly stay in the heart of Äkäslompolo - an unspoilt Lappish gem.</p>
<h2>Excellent quality Apartments</h2>
<p>Discover our highly recommended and well-equipped apartments in <a data-udi="umb://document/8d7194d440db47e2b48d371f537fb9db" href="/{localLink:umb://document/8d7194d440db47e2b48d371f537fb9db}" title="Santa Breaks in Yllas">Ylläs</a>, located in a peaceful and scenic setting. Each apartment has its own fully equipped kitchen, wood-burning fire and sauna, which is ideal for warming up after a day of adventures, making these apartments an excellent choice for your <a data-udi="umb://document/63d3751ab6044b7c82e72f82f4d64e39" href="/{localLink:umb://document/63d3751ab6044b7c82e72f82f4d64e39}" title="Lapland/Finland">Lapland</a> visit.</p>
<h2>Village centre at your fingertips</h2>
<p>With a convenient 5-10 minute walk (500 meters), you'll find yourself in the village centre. Immerse yourself in the local culture and explore the hidden treasures of Äkäslompolo. The apartments <span>are available self-catered or with an optional half board upgrade. They're all well-equipped with kitchen facilities and there's a well-stocked supermarket in the village centre, along with cafes, shops and restaurants. You'll also have the choice to upgrade to half board, where you can enjoy hearty buffet style breakfasts and dinners in the Akas Hotel restaurant. </span></p>
<h2>Santa programme and excursions</h2>
<p>Get ready for a memorable Santa experience and exciting excursions in <a data-udi="umb://document/8d7194d440db47e2b48d371f537fb9db" href="/{localLink:umb://document/8d7194d440db47e2b48d371f537fb9db}" title="Santa Breaks in Yllas">Ylläs</a>! <span>Lapland is one of the best places in the world to witness the Northern Lights and staying in the Ylläs during the winter months provides an excellent opportunity to witness this natural phenomenon. The apartments are a great base to enjoy our optional extra activities such as snowmobiling, reindeer and husky rides and snow shoeing. Plus after a day of exploring, you can unwind in your apartments private sauna or by the fireplace.</span></p>]]></description>
